### ============================================
### 8. VERIFICAÇÕES FINAIS
### ============================================

### 8.1 Ver saldo atual do FAC
GET http://localhost:3000/groups/{{groupIdFAC}}/saldos
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenSuper}}

### 8.2 Ver saldo atual do JOAM
GET http://localhost:3000/groups/{{groupIdJOAM}}/saldos
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenSuper}}

### 8.3 Ver transações do FAC
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions/group/{{groupIdFAC}}
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenWalber}}

### 8.4 Ver transações do JOAM
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions/group/{{groupIdJOAM}}
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenJP}}

### 8.5 Ver todas transações (Super Admin)
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenSuper}}

